</span>“我要幸福”<span class="_ _e"></span>是没用的。<span class="_ _e"></span>如果大家能按照<span class="_ _e"></span>《修</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 ya6 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">心八颂》调整自心，我敢保证各位的幸福感会日益提升。 </div><div class="t m0 x1b h4 ya7 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls14 ws0">或许有人怀疑：<span class="_ _b"></span><span class="ls15">“这个法只有短短八个偈颂，有那么殊</span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 ya8 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">胜吗？”<span class="_ _7"></span>其实，<span class="_ _e"></span>所谓的秘诀，<span class="_ _7"></span>就是用最简练的语言，<span class="_ _e"></span>开显最</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 ya9 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">甚深的意义，就像一把小钥匙便可以打开大门一样。所以，</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yce ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">大家千万别小看了这八个偈颂。 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
